          img(src=mapurl).fl
      div.fl.tc.pl4.pr5.w-75.lh-copy
        p.f6.tl.mb1.lighttext A monthly update of 
          span.highlight harassment and displacement risk in rent stabilized buildings
          span  in 
          span.medtext #{district.borough} #{district.name}
          span . Risk indicators include 
        div
          ol.tl.mt1.f6.lighttext 
            li
              a(href='#sales') New sales of residential buildings
            li 
              a(href='#hpdcomplaints') Five or more new complaints filed with the Department of Housing Preservation and Development (HPD)
            li 
              a(href='#hpdviols') Ten or more new violations issued by HPD
            li 
              a(href='#dobcomplaints') Two or more new complaints filed with the Department of Buildings (DOB)
            li 
              a(href='#dobjobs') New DOB construction permit applications.
        p.f6.tl.mb1.lighttext
          span  Buildings that appear on multiple lists are coded 
          span.dapyellow.black.ph1 yellow
          span , 
          span.daporange.black.ph1 orange
          span , or 
          span.dapred.white.ph1.lighttext red
          span , based on the number of lists they're on.
        p.f6.tl.lighttext.no-print The 
         span.fakelink blue links
         span  let you click through directly to a property's 
         a(href='http://whoownswhat.justfix.nyc', target='_blank') Who Owns What
         span  page for owner info, 
         a(href='https://hpdonline.hpdnyc.org/HPDonline/provide_address.aspx', target='_blank') HPD building info
         span , 
         a(href='http://a810-bisweb.nyc.gov/bisweb/bispi00.jsp', target='_blank') DOB's Building Information System
         span ,  
         a(href='https://a836-acris.nyc.gov/DS/DocumentSearch/BBL', target='_blank') ACRIS financial records
         span , or 
         a(href='http://nycprop.nyc.gov/nycproperty/nynav/jsp/selectbbl.jsp', target='_blank') property tax information
         span . You can also click a building address to view it in Google Maps.
        p.tl.f6.lighttext All buildings listed have registered stabilized units at least once between 2007 and 2016 
          span.no-print (
          a(href='#notes').no-print Notes
          span.no-print ). 
      div.fl.pb3.w-100
        p.tc.mb1.f6.lighttext If a building appears on more than one of the lists below in a given month it will be flagged: 
        table.ph4.w-100
          thead
            tr
              th
                img(src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/aepyornis/dap-dr/master/dashboard/riskyellow.png').risks
              th
                img(src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/aepyornis/dap-dr/master/dashboard/riskorange.png').risks
              th
                img(src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/aepyornis/dap-dr/master/dashboard/riskred.png').risks
        p.tc.mv1.f6.no-print Tip: 
          span.lighttext.no-print to find the building on other lists, copy its BBL and use Find (Ctrl+F or &#8984+F)
    div.fl.w-100.pt3.ph4.pb2.bg-black-10#sales
      p.f3.tl.mt0.mb1 New sales of residential buildings last month
      p.f6.tl.mt0.mb3.lighttext.lh-copy A high sale price can mean the new owner plans to displace existing tenants to make more profit. 
        | Buildings on this list sold for more than $50,000, which is used as a threshold for "true" sales versus other types of transfers. 
        span.no-print (
        a(href='#notes') Notes
        span.no-print ).  Sales data is messy â€“ click a building's 
        a(href='https://a836-acris.nyc.gov/DS/DocumentSearch/BBL', target='_blank').no-print (ACRIS)
        span.no-print  link for more detailed documentation. 
        span.medtext Note: 
        span data from the Department of Finance can lag, so these sales might be from the month before last. 
      table.w-100
        thead
          tr
            th.w-10 BBL
            th.w-20 Address
            th.w-15 Total Units
            th.w-10(colspan="2").f5 Stabilized Units
            th.f5.w-5.tc Sale Price
            th.f5.w-5.tc Price / Sq Foot
