      p.f6.tl.mt0.mb3.lighttext.lh-copy Complaints that tenants make about conditions in their apartment or building get sent to Housing Preservation and Development for inspection. One complaint can include multiple problems in an apartment or a building. 
        span.no-print Click a building's 
        a(href='https://hpdonline.hpdnyc.org/HPDonline/provide_address.aspx', target='_blank').no-print (HPD)
        span.no-print  link for details. 
